#BlueJ class context
comment0.target=VehicleWorld
comment0.text=\n\ Written\ task,\ I\ have\ the\ markdown\ version\ for\ it.\ If\ you\ want\ to\ see\ it,\ the\ file\ name\ is\:\ WrittenTask.md\n\ \#\ 1.\ Included\ a\ detailed\ description\ of\ features.\ What\ am\ I\ about\ to\ watch?\n\ You\ are\ watching\ for\ __something__\:\n\ >\ There\ are\ four\ vehicles\ in\ the\ simulation\:\ Ambulance,\ Mine\ Cleaner,\ IFV\ (nfantry\ fighting\ vehicle)\ and\ Tank\ \\\n\ >\ Tank\ and\ IFV\ use\ a\ separate\ rotating\ tower\n\n\ >\ >\ The\ Complex\ intelligennt\ gun\ tower\\\n\ >\ >\ It\ will\ shoot\ unseen\ scout\ shell\ to\ aim\ for\ the\ enemy\ (Mine\ Dropper)\\\n\ >\ >\ If\ hit\ friendly\ side,\ stop\ shooting\ real\ shell\\\n\ >\ >\ If\ hit\ the\ emeny,\ shout\ live\ shell\n\n\ >\ Ambulance\ heals\ injured\ pedestrian\ \\\n\ >\ Mine\ Cleaner\ stopes\ to\ remove\ mines\ from\ the\ road\ \\\n\ >\ Civilian\ tries\ to\ cross\ the\ road\ safely\ \\\n\ >\ MineDropper\ acts\ as\ an\ enemy\ and\ place\ mines\ in\ road\ lanes\n\ >\ I\ implemented\ advaced\ lane\ changing\ using\ trigonometry\\\n\ >\ The\ Gun\ towr\ rotate\ towards\ the\ target\\\n\ >\ After\ enough\ Mine\ Dropper\ were\ killed,\ it\ will\ trigger\ a\ air\ strike\\\n\ >\ JDAMs\ will\ be\ droppped\ into\ the\ world,\ destroy\ all\ the\ vehicles.\n\n\ \#\ Description\ of\ world\ and\ local\ effect\n\ \#\#\ World\ Effect\n\ After\ enough\ mine\ droppers\ were\ killed,\ a\ warning\ will\ pop\ up\ on\ the\ screen\ "Air\ Strike\ Arived"\\\n\ After\ 2\ seconds,\ a\ f15\ will\ fly\ over\ the\ world.\ \\\n\ 1\ second\ later,\ JDAM(Joint\ Direct\ Attack\ Munition)s\ will\ hit\ all\ the\ vehicles.\ Completely\ destroy\ them.\n\n\ \#\#\ Local\ Effect\n\ A\ local\ effect\ project\ is\ explosion.\ \\\n\ Explosions\ are\ triggered\ by\ mines,\ shells,\ destroy\ vehicles\ and\ air\ strikes.\ \\\n\ Explosions\ only\ affected\ a\ limited\ area\ for\ a\ limited\ of\ time.\ \\\n\ The\ explosion\ also\ effect\ nearby\ pedestrians\n\n\ \#\ Description\ of\ Which\ Vehicles\ Change\ Lanes\ and\ Under\ What\ Conditions\n\ Tank,\ IFV,\ and\ Ambulance\ use\ the\ default\ change\ lane\ algorithm\ and\ Mine\ Cleaner\ uses\ a\ special\ lane\ change\ algorithm.\\\n\ Vehicles\ try\ to\ change\ lanes\ when\ a\ slow\ vehicle\ is\ ahead\ of\ them.\\\n\ The\ vehicle\ change\ lane\ with\ some\ conditions\:\n\ >\ A\ vehicle\ only\ change\ lane\ if\ there\ is\ a\ slower\ vehilce\ ahead\ of\ them\ or\ this\ is\ a\ mine\ ahead\ of\ them\ (does\ not\ work\ for\ mine\ Cleaner)\\\n\ >\ Each\ changing\ lane\ will\ be\ finsihed\ in\ 21\ acts\\\n\ >\ Each\ vehicle\ only\ change\ lane\ if\ the\ lane\ vehicle\ intends\ to\ change\ has\ no\ parallel\ vehicle\n\n\ \#\ Known\ BUGS\n\ In\ very\ complex\ scene,\ the\ FPS\ could\ have\ occasional\ frame-rate\ drop.\\\n\ Two\ pedestrians\ may\ overlap\ together.\\\n\ Vehicle\ may\ intend\ to\ change\ lane\ without\ safe\ direction\ from\ the\ ahead\ vehicle.\ And\ they\ crash\ together.\ And\ disappear.\ \\\n\ I\ nearly\ reach\ the\ greenfoot\ limit,\ it\ is\ better\ to\ use\ unity\ and\ C\#\ to\ code\ the\ program.\n\n\ \#\ Credits\n\ I\ use\ codex\ to\ debug\ my\ and\ create\ certain\ codes.\ They\ are\:\n\ >\ Vehicleworld.java\ to\ avoid\ pedestrians\ spawn\ on\ the\ rock\ in\ my\ background\\\n\ >\ Pedestrian.java\ used\ for\ movement\ checking\ against\ Pedestrian's\ overlap\ with\ rocks\ in\ background\\\n\ >\ Tower.java\ for\ improved\ performance\\\n\ >\ ScreenMessage.java\ created\ by\ codex\\\n\ >\ JDAM\ Draw\ by\ codex\n\ >\ background\n\n\ By\ Jordan\ Cohen\:\n\ >\ SuperSmoothMover.java\ class\\\n\ >\ TrailPiece.java\ Class\\\n\ >\ Counter.java\ class\\\n\ >\ Started\ code\ template\n\n\ Resources\ generated\ by\ gemini\:\n\ >\ Civilian\ \\\n\ >\ Mine\ Dropper\ \\\n\ >\ LandMine\ \\\n\ >\ Ambulance\ \\\n\ >\ Mine\ Cleaner\ \\\n\ >\ F15\n\n\ https\://free-game-assets.itch.io/free-2d-tank-game-assets\n\ >\ Tank,\ IFV,\ Tank\ Tower,\ IFV\ Tower\n\n\ \#\#\ Sound\ Effects\:\n\ >\ background.mp3\:\ StarWar\:\ https\://www.youtube.com/watch?v\=Z8rl7L4-YPM&t\=607s\ \\\n\ >\ AirJet\ sound\:\ https\://pixabay.com/sound-effects/film-special-effects-fighter-jet-powerful-low-flyby-sfx-337205/\ \\\n\ >\ shooting\ sound\:\ https\://pixabay.com/sound-effects/film-special-effects-machine-gun-burst-43670/\ \\\n\ >\ explosion\ sound\:https\://mixkit.co/free-sound-effects/explosion/\ \\\n\ >\ alarm\ sound\:\ https\://pixabay.com/sound-effects/film-special-effects-beep-warning-6387/\ \\\n\ >\ pickup\ sound\:\ created\ by\ gemini\ \ \\\n\ >\ Drop\ Mine\ sound\:\ https\://pixabay.com/sound-effects/film-special-effects-hard-object-drop-98768/\n
